Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hello, Higurashi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagome's grandpa!\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that you, Yuka?\NWhy hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Is Kagome home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:54.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Kagome pulled her\nback again and took to her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pulled her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who pulled her back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,May I speak to Kagome please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Kagome's diabetes\ncame back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! Has she been\nhospitalized again for tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beriberi and rheumatism\nand neuralgia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's such a sickly\ngrandchild...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you cut it out, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would a girl my age\nget neuralgia and rheumatism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to tell lies, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm just helping to explain\nyour absence...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when you go off\nto the Feudal Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what I'm saying is valid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:43.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way! I'm right here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes... Kagome, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You usually rush off over to\nthe other side on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I made up\nthose illnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what's wrong with staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This world is where I really belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota! Playing games\nfrom morning again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The weather's great, so\ngo outside to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you go to the movies\nwith me on Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be a nice change\nfrom studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in love with someone else,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Game over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:50.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}l- I didn't come here because\NI was worried about Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... I'm going on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's been thrown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha denied it, but he's not\nback to full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How come he's so strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:34.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A huge Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time to show them my...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:05.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Split Image!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's slight, but\NI feel the presence of the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After I came back all\nthe way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! The time!\NI'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:14.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Inuyasha!\N- He usually fights back so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:39.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His slow movements aren't\nsimply due to his injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:45.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without Kagome, he's unable to\nrealize his true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Royakan definitely is\nusing the power of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find where it is,\nand you can defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome would know\nits weak spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where the fragment is hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:03.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget about her.\NKagome's not here anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I closed up the well which\nconnected her world to ours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-she will never return\nhere again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,involve Kagome in\nthese dangerous battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:21.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:36.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cripes...he gets me so mad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always interfered when I\n{\i1}had a test and was cramming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi, what's the matter?\NYou look so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? l-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. I'm on a date.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I thinking of that\nfool at such a time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:54.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... What were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you forcing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forcing myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I keep thinking about him...\nam I being too proud?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no... no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can sorta tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo... I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think anything of him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet you don't feel well,\nbut you forced yourself to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your grandfather said you had gout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even to Hojo too...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I look sick at all?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right... Maybe Inuyasha's\nwound hasn't healed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh{\i0} no... {\i1}What if he's dead?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hojo! Ask me out again.\NGood bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel it!\NI feel the Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where? Where is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to go back!\NInuyasha, are you all right?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fragment of the\NSacred Jewel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was able to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I smell Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!\NKagome is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:21.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't... get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's suddenly much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! At least deliver the\nfatal blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's wound isn't\nfully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The enemy is taking\nadvantage of that to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew{\i0} it... {\i1}He's in danger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly fool!\NW-why'd you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:29.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought you died... because\nyou didn't come for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you not to come anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:39.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't help it!\NI longed to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Longed to see me? Me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...l...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to see me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you?! I was so worried\nabout you... What a fool I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-hey! Are you crying, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't cry over such a trifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:07.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not crying out of sadness!\NIt's frustration!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They fight the minute they set\neyes on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:13.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But thank goodness it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede, it's Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess Kaede?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monk, don't you think it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:26.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The droves of poison insects have\ndisappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo?\NNo, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo... That woman died\nfifty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- what is this presence?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone's here... who possesses\nthe Sacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lots of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew you were nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:34.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...he is Naraku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before I kill you, I must ask\nyou one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What grudge do you have\nagainst me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grudge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you can't\ndie in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:15.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,not knowing why someone\nhates you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:18.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kaede, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My, my... How old you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it... You are... Onigumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Onigumo... Such a nostalgic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Naraku, am not Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:43.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it is true... that fifty years ago,\NI was borne out of Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onigumo was a foolish man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He began to desire the kind-hearted\nyoung priestess who nursed him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He succumbed to his weakness\nand called forth the demons...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even my rotting soul is\nworth something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Want a taste of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hungry for me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want a body that moves freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:26.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to possess the\NSacred Jewel and Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now eat me! Devour me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:34.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And in return, give me power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is how...many demons\nbecame one...into Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Creating my body took\ncountless demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because the priestess had been\nreduced to a powerless girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}this region teemed with demons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All because the priestess...Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:20.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}had fallen in love with\na worthless half-demon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She gave in to childish desires...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}tried to use the power\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and was punished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}you experienced the\npunishment yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:16.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid fool! I have no desire\nto become human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You tricked Kikyo and me\ninto trying to kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let me ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Was the trust you had in each\nother so easy to destroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The truth is that anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bitter anger set you against\neach other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is the true legacy of\nthe trust you had for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo could not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Instead of choosing death...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,she should have clung on to\nher life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and used the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Had she pleaded for her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,her wretched wish would have\nbeen easily granted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and she would have understood\nthe ultimate truth of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Such a foolish woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:16.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel grows even more\nbeautiful when it is tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:30.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many fragments do you see\ninside him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel fragments...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ten... No, twenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:44.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Naraku... I'll show you\nwhat tainted is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make that tainted blood\nof yours flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A miasma! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've sunken into\nmy miasma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,cut through the miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That damned Naraku got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A spider on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. According to Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:55.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a spider-shaped burn mark\non his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The robber Onigumo had\nterrible burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps that is proof that\nit is Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A spider on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That will also be the\ntelltale sign of Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are asked to protect the souls\nof the dead people at a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:55.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon gathers numbers of souls\nand carries them away to somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demon is controlled by a priestess\nwith an awful vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A priestess?\NCould she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nobody can sooth her\nanger and sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where are they taking her to?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha: "A Wicked {\b1}smile;{\b0}\NKikyo's Wandering Soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
